### Create a new chat session
POST http://localhost:8008/api/v1/chats
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "test_user_1"
}

### Poll chat session (replace {sessionId} with actual value)
GET http://localhost:8008/api/v1/chats/{sessionId}/poll

### Get API status
GET http://localhost:8008/api/v1/chats/status

